Description_lang: Hurls arcane energy toward the target, inflicting $s1 Arcane damage and granting a stack of Arcane Surge, increasing attack and cast speed by $s3%.At 5 stacks, Arcane Surge will cause an Arcane Burst, inflicting $s1 Arcane damage to all players.
AuraDescription_lang: Building arcane energy.Attack and cast speed increased by $s3%.Detonates at 5 stacks.
